extends layouts/main

block content
    section.section.section--visual
    .inner
        .summary
        .summary__title
            | 🎁 특별한 선물 GIFT&nbsp;WEB 
        .summary__description
            | 친구들 또는 가족과 함께 소중한 사람만을 위한 웹페이지를 선물해보세요.
        form#sign-form(action='' method='POST')
        ul
            li
            input.input--text(type='text' placeholder='Pick a Username')
            li
            input.input--text(type='email' placeholder='Your email address')
            li
            input.input--text(type='password' placeholder='Create a Password')
            p.caption nickname은 선물상자와 함께 표시됩니다.
            li
            button.btn.btn--primary(type='submit') Start GIFT-WEB
            p.caption 이메일은 본인을 식별하는데만 사용됩니다. 기존 이메일주소와 같은 비밀번호를 사용하지 않는 것을 권장합니다.
    // FEATURE
    section.section.section--feature
    .summary
        .summary__title
        | 새로운 선물 문화
        .summary__description
        | 선물하는 사람과 받는 사람 모두 재밌고 의미 있는 GITWEB Service에 오신 것을 환영합니다! ✨
    .video
        .video-ratio
        iframe(width='1078' height='606' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/afvT1c1ii0c' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture' allowfullscreen='')
    .tiles
        .inner
        ul.clearfix
            li
            img(src='./img/feature-tile__build.png' alt='')
            h3 For everything you build
            p
                | Host and manage your code on GitHub. You can keep your work private or share it with the world.
            li
            img(src='./img/feature-tile__work.png' alt='')
            h3 A better way to work
            p
                | From hobbyists to professionals, GitHub helps developers simplify the way they build software.
            li
            img(src='./img/feature-tile__projects.png' alt='')
            h3 Millions of projects
            p
                | GitHub is home to millions of open source projects. Try one out or get inspired to create your
                | own.
            li
            img(src='./img/feature-tile__platform.png' alt='')
            h3 One platform, from start to finish?
            p
                | With hundreds of integrations, GitHub is flexible enough to be at the center of your development
                | process.
